CREATE TABLE transactions (transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, account_id INT REFERENCES accounts(account_id), transaction_type STRING, amount DECIMAL(10, 2), transaction_date DATE)</t><stat>select * from users join accounts on users.id = accounts.user_id join transactions on accounts.account_id = transactions.account_id</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE categories (category_id INT PRIMARY KEY, category_name STRING, parent_category_id INT REFERENCES categories(category_id))
